{"tid":940765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李國章續任港大校委員會主席　任期三年","createTime":"2018-12-14T07:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T07:54:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acd73339c7b512dcc3fb225f4ed9f5bab8892169","tid":940765,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:54:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433290-20181214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433290-20181214.htm&d=UjbqDZMb4GeaL7OhZmVf2xxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=c1d85356\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433290-20181214.htm&h=41d40f8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433290-20181214.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cn8vOXtVUAAZOKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCn8vOXtVUAAZOKo.jpg&h=8e21b32b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥委任李國章繼續出任香港大學校務委員會主席，由明年1月1日起，為期3年。<br />\n<br />\n香港大學發表聲明表示，校長張翔歡迎李國章續任校委會主席。他說，李國章在大學管治上給予卓越領導，他的續任對推動港大在各領域的發展、實現抱負，一定能作出重要貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n李國章在聲明中表示，非常高興及榮幸可以續任校委會主席，期待繼續和校長、校委會成員和所有港大成員等，努力令港大有更卓越成就。"}]}